Package: readstore
Title: This is the R client (SDK) for the ReadStore API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonathan", "Alles", , "jonathan.alles@evo-byte.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The readstore package can be used to access projects, datasets, metadata and attachment files in the ReadStore Database from R code and scripts.
    The package enables you to automate your bioinformatics pipelines, Python scripts and notebooks.
    The ReadStore API is a RESTful API that allows you to access the ReadStore Database from any programming language.
